profile:
New roofs • Commercial and Residential Roofing

For a professional roofing service on the South Shore and in the Greater Montreal area, call Excellente Toiture Inc’s experienced Team with over 25 years of experience in the field of the roofing!

Excellente Toiture Inc’s meticulous staff specializes in flat roof, roof white TPO membrane on residential and commercial buildings.

The membrane is guaranteed for 20 years and labor has a 10-year guarantee!

APCHQ member, with Excellente Toiture Inc, you know that the work will be done in a clean and respectful manner!

Call for a quote! 450 445-6209

profile: Lakeshore Roofing was established in 1990 serving the West Island for more than 20 years and is recommended and Certified by CAA Habitation, BP Certified and APCHQ Certified, we are fully licensed and insured, we provide Roofing installations, roof repairs, Insulation & Gutter Protection. Each and every one of our professional technicians are thoroughly trained in respect to each of the tasks and have each successfully completed all of the necessary safety (CSST) training involved. Our Company’s goal is to professionally service each of our customer’s to the best of our abilities and in the highest standard possible.
